<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Cancelled - MENTIS</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D62828 0%, #B71C1C 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #FFCDD2;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .cancelled-badge {
            background: #FFEBEE;
            color: #D62828;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .event-card {
            background: #F1F6F4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #D62828;
        }
        .event-card h2 {
            color: #D62828;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .detail-label {
            color: #6B7280;
            width: 120px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #1E1E1E;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #F1F6F4;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6B7280;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2F5D52;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>❌ Registration Cancelled</h1>
            <p>MENTIS Mental Health Platform</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <span class="cancelled-badge">❌ CANCELLED</span>
            
            <p>Dear <strong>{{ registration.userName }}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your registration for the following event has been cancelled as requested.</p>
            
            <div class="event-card">
                <h2>📌 {{ event.title }}</h2>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">📅 Date & Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ event.dateTime|date('l, F d, Y \\a\\t H:i') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">📍 Location:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ event.location|default('Online Event') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">🎫 Ticket:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ registration.ticketType|title }} × {{ registration.numberOfTickets }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you cancelled by mistake or would like to re-register, please visit our events page.</p>
            <p>We hope to see you at future events!</p>
            
            <a href="{{ url('app_event_index') }}" class="button">Browse Events</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} MENTIS - Mental Health Platform</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>